                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Access<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We reserve the right to refuse access to our Service for any reason at
                                    any time. Additionally, we may make modifications and enhancements to our
                                    service at any moment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">How we arrange search engine results<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">There are several travel alternatives accessible via our Service, and we
                                    aim to provide the most relevant search results possible. On the search results
                                    page, you may choose how to order the results and apply filters to prioritize
                                    results depending on your preferences, such as price, guest review score, or
                                    other factors. If you choose not to utilize these features, you will see our
                                    default sort order, which sorts results according to the criteria listed below.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Within your search results, we may also provide travel choices that are
                                    sponsored advertisements from our Travel Providers. As a means of
                                    distinguishing them from other travel alternatives, these travel options are
                                    prominently labeled "Ad" or a similar designation for your knowledge.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Referral and third-party reservation services<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Please keep in mind that if you are routed from our website to a
                                    third-party booking service <span class="GramE">in order to</span> make a trip
                                    reservation, you will be making the reservation with the third-party and not
                                    with us. We are not responsible for reservations made via a third-party booking
                                    service, and we assume no obligation for such reservations. The third-party
                                    service provider's terms and conditions will outline your rights against them
                                    and clarify their obligation to you.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo11"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span></b><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">GENERAL CONDITIONS AND
                                    RULES<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">When you book services via our website, you allow us to serve as your
                                    agent during the booking process with the chosen Travel Provider. You permit us
                                    to pay for the products/services in your name and on your behalf, if necessary.
                                    Depending on whatever product you reserve, we will issue the ticket and charge
                                    you appropriately. The amount you will be charged will be revealed before you
                                    confirm your reservation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The Customer must be required to provide all booking-required
                                    information that is comprehensive and error-free. If the information is
                                    erroneous or a third-party credit card is used for payment processing, we may
                                    demand extra verification.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span class="SpellE"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;
                                    line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;
                                    mso-ansi-language:EN-US">Trippbo</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US"> AB is not liable for
                                    any reschedules or cancellations. The airlines are permitted to change, cancel,
                                    or postpone their flights. Please do not hesitate to let us know if there are
                                    any problems with the Travel services you have purchased via our services. On
                                    our end, we promise to remedy the matter as quickly as feasible.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo11"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">3.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span></b><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">HOTEL TERMS<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF HOTEL<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">As noted under "About these terms," your booking is also
                                    subject to the conditions of the applicable Provider (in this example, the
                                    hotel where you are staying). These are often available on the hotel's website.
                                    If there are any discrepancies between these terms and the hotel's terms and
                                    conditions, such as if you choose a cheaper accommodation that cannot be
                                    altered or returned, these terms shall govern. As part of our customer support
                                    services, if you have any queries about the terms and conditions that apply to
                                    your hotel reservation, you may contact us directly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">BOOKING PROCESS<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Within the time range we advised you of throughout your booking
                                    procedure, we will make a reasonable effort to provide you a confirmation of
                                    your hotel reservation. If your hotel reservation confirmation has not been
                                    received within this timeframe, please contact us. Many of our accommodations
                                    provide instantaneous confirmation. We will send you an email as soon as your
                                    reservation is confirmed to let you know that your accommodation is assured. If
                                    we are unable to confirm your reservation, you will get a full refund.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Please do not be concerned if, after your hotel reservation has been
                                    confirmed, you call the hotel directly and they are unable to find your reservation.
                                    Your reservation is still secure; however, the hotel may not get your personal
                                    information until closer to the day of your stay. If you have any questions or
                                    issues, please contact us.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">CHANGING, CANCELLING OR UPGRADING YOUR BOOKING<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">During the booking process, we will have informed you of your rights to
                                    amend or cancel your hotel reservation (and any applicable costs); you may have
                                    picked a less expensive accommodation that cannot be modified or returned. This
                                    information is part of these terms and should be carefully reviewed prior to
                                    completing your reservation. If you are uncertain if your hotel reservation
                                    accepts alterations and/or cancellation reimbursements, please contact us.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">When your hotel reservation enables modifications, the hotel or a
                                    third-party hotel inventory provider may restrict the hotels and/or rooms to
                                    which you may switch. As a result, not <span class="GramE">all of</span> the
                                    alternatives on our website and/or alternative rooms at that hotel may be
                                    accessible to you. When we receive your request to modify your hotel
                                    reservation, we will advise you of the potential alternatives.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If the hotel modifies or cancels your reservation, the hotel's terms and
                                    conditions will often apply. Please contact us directly and we will assist you
                                    as part of our customer service.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">HOTEL REVIEWS<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Guests’ ratings are derived on verified user feedback. Star ratings are
                                    based on a variety of factors, including ratings supplied directly by the
                                    hotels (including, where appropriate, their star rating based on the standards
                                    of the country where they are located), facilities, photographs, guest reviews,
                                    and pricing. This will provide you the greatest indicator of the hotel's
                                    quality. However, you acknowledge and agree that the star rating is merely an
                                    indication, that standards vary between countries, and that it is your
                                    responsibility to review all the information provided on the hotel on our website
                                    to ensure that you are satisfied with the hotel's standard prior to booking.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo11"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">4.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span></b><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">FLIGHT TERMS<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF FLIGHT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Agreement and pricing adjustments<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Your booking request will be confirmed through email. At this point, the
                                    mediation contract between you and us becomes official. If you do not get such
                                    confirmation within one hour of submitting your booking request, please call us
                                    to verify.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You will get an email with a ticket number when your tickets are issued.
                                    You and the appropriate airline(s) have signed a binding contract.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The airline adds flight and seat prices on the Portal. If the airline
                                    makes changes outside of our control (e.g., price changes, seat availability,
                                    etc.) after a booking request is made but before the contract with the airline
                                    becomes binding, the contract will not enter into force and your payment will
                                    be refunded in full. We may contact You and offer You the updated price within
                                    normal opening hours, but no later than 24 hours after We learn of the price
                                    change or on the first weekday after that.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Booking and travel conditions<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We are just a middleman for Portal flights. We take no contractual
                                    responsibility for your flight's performance or non-performance. Flight
                                    performance is entirely up to the operating airline.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You'll see the airline(s)' terms and conditions before booking.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We cannot access airline booking systems while mediating airline travel
                                    services. If so, we can sign the airline contract for you. For bookings,
                                    revisions, or cancellations, contact the appropriate low-cost airline directly.
                                    You may get two reservation confirmations, one from us and one from the
                                    airline. Please utilize the low-cost airline reservation confirmation for
                                    check-in if you get two.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We present an overview of airline booking and travel criteria below.
                                    Before booking, verify the airline's terms and conditions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Check-in/flights<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">All flight timings are local. The schedule shows "+1"
                                    arrivals. After the ticket is issued, flight schedules may vary due to flight
                                    control, weather, or airline constraints. Check the time before your flight.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Please observe airline check-in times. Late check-ins might result in
                                    denied boarding. Please note that certain airlines promote online check-in since
                                    they may impose a fee for airport check-in.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Multiple tickets<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Booking two one-way tickets instead of a roundtrip is plainly noted.
                                    Cancellations, modifications, strikes, and flying schedule changes affect
                                    tickets separately. Airlines' rules apply.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Flights with distinct booking numbers are always independent.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Segmented flight tickets<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">One-way or roundtrip tickets may have many portions. Most airlines need
                                    sequenced flight segments. If not, many airlines may deny carriage on future
                                    flights (e.g., failure to use one segment of a journey could invalidate the
                                    rest of the ticket). The airline may cancel your incoming flight if you miss
                                    your outgoing journey on roundtrip tickets.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Pregnancy<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Some airlines refuse to fly pregnant women beyond week 28. Pregnant
                                    women must check with the airline and their doctors before traveling.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Infant/Child tickets<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Contact the airline for information about flying with a youngster
                                    without a seat. Children under 2 <span class="GramE">travel</span> as babies and
                                    do not need their own seat, while children over 2 must. A kid ticket must be
                                    purchased if the newborn turns 2 before the trip ends. Infant tickets cannot be
                                    booked before birth since the passport name and birth date must match. If the
                                    erroneous ticket is bought, we will not cover any costs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Unaccompanied minors<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We do not book unaccompanied child tickets. Under-18s must go with an
                                    adult. Some nations and airlines don't allow under-18s without a guardian. Some
                                    airlines need birth certificates for under-18s.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Lost/damaged baggage<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">As intermediaries, we are not liable for missing or damaged baggage.
                                    Report any issues to the airline's airport agent immediately.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Transit and lodging<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Flight tickets do not include ground transportation or overnight
                                    accommodations. Check ground transportation fares and schedules yourself.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Flight connections<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Standard Portal tickets have authorized connection times. Airlines
                                    calculate connection times. If a flight segment is delayed and causes a missed
                                    connection, airlines must help you reach your destination.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Airlines are not liable for missing connections due to delays when
                                    booking individual tickets. Thus, you must guarantee that airlines and airports
                                    provide enough connecting time. Missed connections will not be refunded.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Double-booking<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Two or more airline reservations with the same passenger’s name are
                                    duplicate bookings. The airline may cancel a duplicate booking (s). Using
                                    various travel agents may also cause this. We are not responsible for aircraft
                                    cancellations or rejected refunds due to duplicate booking.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Dangerous goods<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Hazardous items cannot be carried on airplanes. Violators face five
                                    years in jail and €250,000 fines (49 U.S.C. 5124). Explosives, pressurized
                                    gases, flammable liquids, solids, oxidizers, poisons, corrosives, and
                                    radioactive materials are hazardous. Paints, lighter fluid, pyrotechnics, tear
                                    gases, oxygen bottles, and radiopharmaceuticals. Small amounts (up to 70 ounces
                                    total) of medicines and toiletries in baggage and some smoking materials on
                                    your person are exempt.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">EU-banned airlines (blacklist)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The European Commission and state air transport authorities have banned
                                    several airlines from flying in the EU. Due to safety concerns or inadequate
                                    government oversight, some flights are banned.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">See which airlines are banned here:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Blacklist (List of airlines not permitted to operate in the EU)<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Airline schedules and cancellations<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Symbol;
                                    mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">Your airline may
                                    cancel or change your tickets. The airline will tell us of any changes. As an
                                    added service, we may manage your modification or cancellation refund request
                                    if the airline allows it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Symbol;
                                    mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">Between booking and
                                    travel, your flight timings may vary. To guarantee the flight (and any
                                    connecting flights) departs on time, we suggest staying informed and contacting
                                    your airline at least 72 hours before departure. We are not responsible for
                                    airline schedule changes or their fees.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You-requested cancellations<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Symbol;
                                    mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">The airline, your
                                    contractual partner, sets the terms for modifying flight reservations
                                    (including passenger name, destination, and travel date) and refunds. As
                                    intermediaries, we cannot change such circumstances.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Symbol;
                                    mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">As an added service,
                                    we will manage your booking modification or cancellation refund request if the
                                    airline allows it. We will advise you of any extra service terms while booking.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l8 level1 lfo5"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Symbol;
                                    mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">We must receive your
                                    adjustment requests at least 24 hours before travel to address them (only by
                                    telephone). <o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Contact the airline directly for last-minute changes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Non-Appearance or Absence from the Flight<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You enable us to obtain potential reimbursements from the airline on
                                    your behalf if you fail to present for or attend your scheduled flight. We are
                                    permitted but not required to do so, and your right to obtain unclaimed refunds
                                    directly from the airline is unchanged.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If We are successful in obtaining reimbursements for you, we shall
                                    deduct our costs from the amount recovered. To see our fee schedule, please
                                    click here. We will hold any refunds acquired on your behalf, less our costs,
                                    for 12 months from the flight date. You may request a transfer of this money,
                                    less our fees, at any time prior to the expiration of the 12-month period by
                                    contacting customer care.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Ticketing<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span class="SpellE"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;
                                    line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;
                                    mso-ansi-language:EN-US">Trippbo</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US"> AB will send you an
                                    order confirmation when you book on our website. This email confirms your <span class="SpellE">Trippbo</span> reservation and includes Passenger(s), Itinerary,
                                    and Summary of Charges.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Order confirmations are not electronic tickets. Your e-ticket will
                                    arrive when your reservation is confirmed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Until the booking is ticketed, your reservation's price, availability,
                                    dates, and other terms may vary.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The ability to cancel or change a booked flight is limited and dependent
                                    on the pricing restrictions or other terms and conditions of the airline.
                                    Although certain airlines may provide free ticket cancellations within 24 hours
                                    after ticket issue, this option is restricted for certain rates and ticket
                                    categories. If you desire to cancel your reservation, please contact Customer
                                    Service, and inquire about the ticket's cancellation policy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Many airlines prohibit name changes; thus, if a name change is
                                    necessary, the client must be notified that name changes are only made in
                                    compliance with the airline's policy. Most airlines regard a name change as a
                                    cancellation, for which usual terms and fees apply.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If you seek any changes and/or modification to your original booking due
                                    to force majeure (cancellation or modification), in addition to the terms and
                                    conditions of the airline, the processing costs indicated below will apply.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Post-Ticketing service charges Quoted per passenger<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Void if cancellation is made within 24 hours of booking and results in a
                                    refund or a modification to the reservation €50.00.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Cancellation and refunds after 24 hours but before to the planned
                                    departure of the current trip €150.00.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Changes or swaps to existing tickets before to the planned departure of
                                    the current trip €150.00.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Managing itinerary modifications, such as rebooking to new trip dates or
                                    ticket cancellations and reimbursements €50.00<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Agent-assisted waivers, such as name updates, exclusions to refund and
                                    exchange policies, and no-shows.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">€50.00<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You could be eligible for a partial refund if you cancel your
                                    reservation. In addition to the airline company's cancellation policies, our
                                    usual processing costs will apply.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The refundable amount will be paid back to the original method of
                                    payment; however, the return time is dependent on your bank's policies.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If you have booked any items or services with us, including flights, but
                                    do not check in (no show) or otherwise do not use the bought products or
                                    services, you will not get a refund. Having <span class="SpellE"><span class="GramE">having</span></span> paid for your ticket, however, you may be
                                    eligible for a tax return. This clause is subject to applicable airline policy.
                                    Since you paid for your ticket, you may get a tax return. Airline policy
                                    governs this.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">REFUNDS for passenger cancellations made voluntarily<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We recognize that vacation arrangements might change often. Depending on
                                    your ticket policy, you may be entitled for a partial refund if you cancel your
                                    reservation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Tickets must be canceled at least 24 hours before to the flight's
                                    planned departure time. Passengers whose tickets were not canceled before to
                                    departure, as well as those who missed their flight or did not board after
                                    check-in, may not be entitled for a refund.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Refunds may only be claimed within the ticket's valid time and only if the
                                    tariff regulations of the bought ticket enable it. This may be partly or
                                    entirely non-refundable if you bought a reduced fare.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">For partly used tickets, the refund amount will be adjusted based on the
                                    unused sector, if allowed by the airline's rules. If there is no remaining
                                    value on the ticket, any unused tax will be returned.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If your ticket is not qualified for a refund, we will provide you with
                                    alternate choices according on the tariff restrictions (e-credit or exchange if
                                    available).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Additional flight services bought from third parties (e.g., insurance,
                                    airport transportation) are not immediately canceled when the ticket is
                                    refunded. To terminate these services, please contact the respective
                                    third-party service provider directly. The purchase of extra flying services
                                    from us is non-refundable.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Schedule Modifications and Unwilling Cancellation<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If the Carrier cancels or fails to operate a flight at the originally
                                    planned time, you will have the option to choose one of the alternative travel
                                    arrangements provided. We will notify you of any important changes as soon as
                                    we become aware of them, but we accept no responsibility for any resulting
                                    modifications or expenses.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You will be able to choose between accepting the time change or a new
                                    travel plan provided by the airline. If the modifications are unacceptable, you
                                    may be eligible for a refund in line with the Conditions of Carriage. If you
                                    are eligible for a rebooking or refund, a processing charge of €50.00 per
                                    person will apply, in addition to the subtraction of non-refundable costs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The airline will provide a different travel arrangement or a time
                                    adjustment. The Conditions of Carriage allow you to request a refund if the
                                    modifications are unacceptable. Our €50 processing charge per person and
                                    non-refundable costs apply to rebooking’s and refunds.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Non-refundable fees<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Administrative Fees, Tips, and Support Packages are non-refundable. The
                                    cardholder's reimbursement will be reduced by any airline penalty or
                                    cancellation charge, which is non-refundable.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Our company has no control over the airline's cancel/change/refund
                                    procedure. Nevertheless, the processing cost paid to execute your request,
                                    which is not the airline’s price to cancel/change/refund the ticket, is a
                                    service offered by our firm and cannot be refunded.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Timing of Refund Processing<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">In rare occasions, tickets may be returned through Cheque or PayPal. We
                                    will give refunds for valid tickets purchased with a credit or debit card
                                    within 20 business days, but this does not include your bank's processing
                                    period.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

