                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">PACKAGES TERMS<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF PACKAGES<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You may book various Travel Services simultaneously using our Service
                                    (such as a hotel reservation and an airline reservation), but each Travel
                                    Service is subject to its own Rules and Restrictions and these Terms (such a
                                    combined booking is a “Package”).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Bookings of multi-packages with several agreements<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If your reservation is a multi-package as described below, we will
                                    function as the "package organizer" and your rights and benefits will
                                    be governed by applicable legislation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l5 level1 lfo7"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Symbol;
