                                    EN-US"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">·<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                                    </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir="LTR"></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;
                                    mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:EN-US">other tourist services
                                    that are not already included in the travel services, provided that these
                                    travel services are purchased in one and the same visit to our website and that
                                    you select them prior to agreeing to pay; or they are advertised, sold, or
                                    charged at an all-inclusive or total price; or they are advertised or sold
                                    under the designation "package" or similar.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">This is referred to as a multi-package since you are entering into
                                    separate agreements with each individual provider/trader of these travel
                                    services. As a package organizer, <span class="SpellE">Trippbo</span> AB will
                                    assume responsibility for this reservation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">NOTE: If you only book one of the travel services listed in (a) - (c)
                                    above in combination with one or more tourist services listed in above, this
                                    will not be considered a multi-package if the tourist services: - does not
                                    constitute 25% of the total value of the combination and is not marketed as, or
                                    otherwise constitutes, an essential part of the package; or - is selected and
                                    purchased after the use of transport, accommodation, or rental car has
                                    commenced. These reservations will subsequently be regarded "single travel
                                    services" and will not be subject to the rights.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We will continue to serve as an agent on behalf of the supplier/trader
                                    for your chosen travel services when you order a multi-package, but we will
                                    perform our legal duties under the PTR as your package organizer. These
                                    responsibilities are outlined in section B of our booking terms. This will have
                                    no effect on our job as the supplier's/representative. trader's<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">To order<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You have the option to examine and confirm all booking information prior
                                    to making payment at the time of booking. Once you have checked and verified
                                    the information and made the necessary payment, we will make the reservation
                                    with the supplier/trader.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Group reservations<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">If you are reserving for a bigger group and want to guarantee that there
                                    are adequate travel services available for everyone, please call our contact <span class="SpellE">centre</span>. If two members of the same group make two separate
                                    online reservations, and availability runs out between the two reservations, we
                                    cannot cancel the first reservation without charging cancellation costs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

