                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">To book your selected travel services, you must first pay according to
                                    the instructions in this clause, or otherwise as requested by the supplier/provider.
                                    You must also pay all applicable insurance premiums and booking fees.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

