                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">We currently do not accept partial payments.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:
                                    107%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Rights in tour packages<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">In accordance with Directive (EU) 2015/2302<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Before entering the package, travelers will be provided with all
                                    necessary information.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">There is always at least one merchant accountable for ensuring that all
                                    agreed-upon travel services are carried out accurately.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">The travelers are provided with an emergency telephone number or contact
                                    information for the organizer or travel agency.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">Transferring a package vacation to another individual is possible with
