                                    mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:
                                    EN-US">You acknowledge that our Group of Companies does not collect taxes for
                                    remittance to taxing authorities, except as provided below with respect to tax
                                    obligations on the amounts received from you, including facilitation fees and
                                    service fees where applicable in accordance. The tax recovery costs for Pay Now
                                    reservations are a reimbursement of the projected taxes that our Group of
                                    Companies pays to the Travel Provider for taxes owed on the Travel Provider's
                                    services (such as for the rental rate for the room). The Travel Providers are
                                    responsible for remitting taxes to the relevant taxation authorities. The
                                    taxability of assets and the relevant tax rate vary substantially by
                                    jurisdiction. Depending on the rates, taxability, etc. in place at the time of
                                    the actual usage of the services supplied by the Travel Provider, the actual
                                    amounts paid by our Group of Companies to the Travel Providers may differ from
                                    the tax recovery fee amounts.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
