                                    EN-US">In some jurisdictions, sales, use, and/or municipal hotel occupancy
                                    taxes are levied on the sums that our Group of Companies charges for services
                                    (service fee and/or facilitation fee). The actual cost charged for services
                                    rendered by our Group of Companies may vary based on the tariffs in place at
                                    the time the Travel Provider renders the services. In some countries, our Group
                                    of Companies is responsible for collecting and remitting sales, use, and/or
                                    municipal hotel occupancy taxes on the whole price, which includes the amounts
                                    we charge for our services and the Travel Services supplied by the Travel
                                    Provider.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

                                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:107%;
