                    <div>
                        <p class="mb-0 fs_14 txt_blue_secondary fw_gilroy_medium line_height_18">The prices for the flight, as well as seat availability, are inserted directly by the relevant airline in the Portal. At the airline's changes that are beyond our control (such as changes in price, seat availability or otherwise) such as occurs after the booking request has been submitted, but before the agreement with the airline has become binding (according to as stated in clause 3.1.2 above), the agreement will not enter into force and your payment will be refunded in full. The we may contact you and give you the opportunity to approve the changed price during normal opening hours, however, no later than 24 hours after We have become aware of the price change or the first weekday after such a 24- hourly period.</p>
